<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>所有文章 - monkvan</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/</link><description>老梵的个人随笔和思考</description><generator>Hugo 0.160.1 &amp; FixIt v0.4.5</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 12:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>梵天：创世神的诞生与陨落</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/brahma-rise-and-fall/</link><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 12:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/brahma-rise-and-fall/</guid><description>&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="梵天创世神的诞生与陨落"&gt;&lt;span&gt;梵天：创世神的诞生与陨落&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e6%a2%b5%e5%a4%a9%e5%88%9b%e4%b8%96%e7%a5%9e%e7%9a%84%e8%af%9e%e7%94%9f%e4%b8%8e%e9%99%a8%e8%90%bd" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：梵天、创世神、三相神、金卵创世、辩才天女、湿婆诅咒、四面佛、印度神话、婆罗门教、宇宙观&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;在印度神话的三相神之中，创造之神梵天的地位最为尊崇，却也最为尴尬。他被称为“众生之父”，从金卵中破壳而出，将天地一分为二，创造了世间万物。然而，全印度供奉他的神庙屈指可数，信众寥寥无几，远不及湿婆与毗湿奴的辉煌。一个创造世界的至高神，为何沦落到如此地步？他被湿婆砍掉头颅的传说背后，藏着怎样的伦理纠葛？他与辩才天女的爱恨情仇，又为何成为他最终失势的转折点？本文将从梵天的诞生、创世、爱恨纠葛到最终的边缘化，完整还原这位创世神的来龙去脉。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>印度神话整体框架</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/indian-mythology-framework/</link><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 12:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/indian-mythology-framework/</guid><description>&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="印度神话整体框架从种姓到宇宙的终极图景"&gt;&lt;span&gt;印度神话整体框架：从种姓到宇宙的终极图景&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%8d%b0%e5%ba%a6%e7%a5%9e%e8%af%9d%e6%95%b4%e4%bd%93%e6%a1%86%e6%9e%b6%e4%bb%8e%e7%a7%8d%e5%a7%93%e5%88%b0%e5%ae%87%e5%ae%99%e7%9a%84%e7%bb%88%e6%9e%81%e5%9b%be%e6%99%af" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：印度神话、种姓制度、三相神、轮回业报、宇宙观、梵我合一、湿婆、毗湿奴、梵天、吠陀经典&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;提起印度神话，很多人会想到象头神、湿婆的第三只眼，或者长达数万行的史诗《摩诃婆罗多》。但这些零散的印象背后，藏着一套完整的世界观——它将社会不平等解释为神意，把人类寿命从四百岁压缩到一百岁，还让宇宙每隔四百三十二万年毁灭一次。更令人惊讶的是，印度教的时间尺度远远超过现代宇宙学：梵天的一天等于八十六点四亿年，而他的寿命长达三百一十一万亿年。这一切究竟如何构建起来的？为什么种姓制度能与轮回说无缝衔接？三相神——创造、维持、毁灭——为何缺一不可？本文将从社会基础、核心教义、宇宙时间、神祇体系和经典来源五个层面，还原印度神话的整体框架。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title/><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/india/%E6%A2%B5%E5%A4%A9%E9%85%8D%E5%81%B6/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/india/%E6%A2%B5%E5%A4%A9%E9%85%8D%E5%81%B6/</guid><description/></item><item><title/><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/india/%E6%AF%97%E6%B9%BF%E5%A5%B4/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/india/%E6%AF%97%E6%B9%BF%E5%A5%B4/</guid><description/></item><item><title/><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/india/%E6%B9%BF%E5%A9%86/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/india/%E6%B9%BF%E5%A9%86/</guid><description/></item></channel></rss>